%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
# Flower generator
Here is a basic example of MarkovJunior used to procedurally grow flowers.

Load the library first:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
PacletDirectoryLoad[
  NotebookDirectory[]//ParentDirectory
];
Needs["CoffeeLiqueur`Workshop`MarkovJunior`"->"mj`"];

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
:::note
Change `PacletDirectoryLoad` directory to match your path to a library or install it globally
:::

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
:::note
Change `PacletDirectoryLoad` directory to match your path to a library or install it globally
:::

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Create a set of rules following the pattern

```
{
  All | 1,  (* apply rule to all found matches or 1 randomly taken *)
  _Integer | Infinity, (* max. number of steps for set of rules *)
                       (* symmetry operations allowed *)
  Automatic | All | None | "Mirror" | ...,
  {
    a -> b,  (* rule 1 *)
    c -> d   (* rule 2 *)
    ...
  }
}
```

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Create a set of rules following the pattern

```
{
  All | 1,  (* apply rule to all found matches or 1 randomly taken *)
  _Integer | Infinity, (* max. number of steps for set of rules *)
                       (* symmetry operations allowed *)
  Automatic | All | None | "Mirror" | ...,
  {
    a -> b,  (* rule 1 *)
    c -> d   (* rule 2 *)
    ...
  }
}
```

